Name: App Say's
Description:
A fun application which makes you smile with its out of context yet hilarious replies. 

How often do we think to lovingly abuse our friends and want to think of that unique humorous thing to say to them.  

App says "I can help." 

App Says is a mix of some hilarious replies to your questions, search for some crude humor with a mix of some innovative emoticons and some sound bites which you would love to play repeatedly. 
 
App Says also lets you add your own words and its meaning to its collection of notorious words and share it with other App Says users. 

Download it, have fun and Cheers !!!

Name: Say Cheesecake
Description:
Homemade decadent cheesecakes in over 50 flavors!  

Since 2012, I have been providing my customers with the most fresh and decadent cheesecake they have ever had!  My recipe is tried & true and loved by many!

With multiple sizes and an abundance of flavors, I can fulfill any order.  Whether you are buying my 2 Shooters or a large spread for a wedding, rest assured that you will receive a freshly made cheesecake and made with only the best ingredients.

When ordering please allow up to 24hrs to confirm your order.  All orders must be placed at least 48hrs in advance.  Everything is freshly made, just for you!

I appreciate each and every customer and you are why I continue to grow!  Thank you!

Name: Rainbow Puke
Description:
::::: Rainbow Puke ::::::

Help Puky in this crazy game to avoid the clouds and get the potatoes by simply tapping anywhere in the screen to dodge them while puking rainbows all along! 

Features: achievements, leaderboards, social sharing, rainbows, glasses, and probably a cat somewhere ;)

... Voted the best casual experience of 2015 by the Rainbow Together Association ...

...... Winner of most funniest app on the Puke Olympics of 1986 ...

.... Reviewed as an awesome crazy casual game by the A Box per Cat Foundation...

WARNING: It may contain traces of POTATO and other tropical vegetables.

Name: Image2Ascii - Convert picture to ASCII Art or Text Art with your favorite letters, Let's say I Love U :-)
Description:
This app converts any images to ASCII Art under gray or color mode, with various resolution. You can set any favorite words to generate the text picture, such as "I Love You Nicole". Show your love now!

Features:
Take a photo from camera or album
You can define any words combination
Support gray and color mode
Support various resolution
Blur motion background and colorful skins

Name: Language Tutor - Pronunciation
Description:
Practice English Pronunciation-Language Tutor
 
Language Tutor is a group of apps which has been developed to assist users to practice their English.
 
Language Tutor – Pronunciation is a handy app that tests and enhances your English pronunciation by using innovative tools. It automatically compares your pronunciation with an American English speaker and creates a score. When you collect enough stars, you level-up!
 
Listen how a native speaker pronounces a word
Repeat the word and record yourself
Get your score and compare your pronunciation
Retry to improve
Collect stars to level-up
 
Wait for the other Language Tutor apps to practice your English.

Name: Let's Talk! - Text Stickers
Description:
Too lazy to type OK? Want to add an extra oomph to your dammit or WTF? Just dunno what to say? 
	Use one of these 32 colourful text stickers - They're gonna talk for you!

	The pack includes...
	- common everyday words (hello, bye, ok, thanks!)
	- stuff to react to any situation (cool, dammit, WTF, wow) 
	- a few for those special occasions in your life (Happy Birthday, congrats)
	- and words to hurry someone up (where are you?, ASAP)
	... AND PLENTY OTHERS

	Created by Marc Ordiali and Edith Kurosaka with the following fonts: Bukhari Script, Forque, and Superpunch. 

	Thank you to all the creators involved in this pack! 
	For words of praise, other comments, or inquiries about getting your own iMessage sticker app, send an email to artists AT feeligo DOT com
